Netas Telekomunikasyon AS, a Turkish
telecommunications company, signed an agreement to buy wholesale
distributor Probil Bilgi Destek & Danismanlik Sanayi & Ticaret
AS for $31 million, Hurriyet reported.  The purchase will help Netas meet its goal of becoming a
leader in systems integration in  Turkey  and the region, the
newspaper said, citing general manager Mujdat Altay.  To contact the reporter on this story:
